        public SkylabClient setIdentityProvider(IdentityProvider provider)

        Sets an identity provider that enriches the SkylabUser with a user_id and device_id when fetching flags. The enrichment happens at the time a new network request is made. This is used to connect Skylab to Amplitude identities.
